  "texts": [
    "As far as item no.",
    "19 is concerned, 53.7 % (SA 20.8 & A 32.9%) said that the contents in English textbooks often offered situations and contexts that they rarely came across in their daily lives.",
    "24.5 % remained neutral.",
    "19 % disagreed and 2.8% strongly opposed the statement.",
    "The mean is 3.5 which is also considered high."
  ]
}